stats is understanding pattern and building insights from data!
there are 4 types of stats
1) descriptive stat - just like the name suggests it tells about the basic description of the data for ex how many rows are there how many columns the shapes means moments modes percentiles everything thats basic comes in form of ddescriptive data
2)inferential stat - in inferential stat it describes the relationship between the columns like how a colum in interrelated between each other ex coverience co relation etc itll understand 
3)predictive stat - it is machine learning using past data to predict future!
4)prescriptive stat - itll prescribe the thoughts and suggestion based on the analysis of the data that wev done in past 
